<h3>How to Build a Prospecting Workflow</h3>
<p>A repeatable workflow prevents wasted effort. Follow this sequence every week:</p>
<ol>
<li>Run competitor gap analysis (Ahrefs or Semrush)</li>
<li>Search for resource pages using Google operators</li>
<li>Check top results for broken links (Check My Links)</li>
<li>Qualify prospects by DA and relevance</li>
<li>Find contact emails (Hunter.io)</li>
<li>Send personalized outreach (BuzzStream or manual)</li>
<li>Track responses and follow up after 5 business days</li>
</ol>
